title: Duminda Silva to leave for Singapore
body_lines: The Housing Development Authority Chairman, Duminda Silva has arrived at Katunayake Airport to depart for Singapore.
He is scheduled to depart for Singapore at 12.50 am tomorrow (7) from Katunayake Airport on Singapore Airlines flight SQ-469.
Sources at the airport said that Duminda Silva had boarded the plane at the moment. (T.K.G. Kapila)
